1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me, my sweet little scheme♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:50,540
=Episode 4=
=Revenge Long in the Making=

11
00:01:06,590 --> 00:01:08,400
Where did this thief come from?

12
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:12,230
I'm your Young Master's wife.

13
00:01:12,590 --> 00:01:13,640
Is this how the Li family

14
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,000
treats its mistress?

15
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,590
Young Master's wife?

16
00:01:17,070 --> 00:01:19,200
The Li family has no such person.

17
00:01:19,310 --> 00:01:21,400
A thief should lose hands and feet
and be dragged to the garden.

18
00:01:22,350 --> 00:01:23,190
Someone come here.

19
00:01:27,070 --> 00:01:28,230
Seize her!

20
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,400
Let's see who dares!

21
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,480
What are you doing?

22
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,840
Ms. Murong.

23
00:01:39,070 --> 00:01:40,070
We just caught a thief.

24
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,280
We're taking her downstairs.

25
00:01:41,380 --> 00:01:43,460
(Murong Xue, Li Hong's fiancée)

26
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,520
Murong Xue.

27
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,320
You know me?

28
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,280
Did Ye Lang tell you about me?

29
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,840
My clothes won't fit you.

30
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:06,040
You'll have to make do with a maid's uniform.

31
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,080
(Any woman who marries into a wealthy family)

32
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:10,000
(is never to be underestimated.)

33
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:15,150
Anyone who violates the Li family's taboos

34
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,520
will end up as

35
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:20,910
their feed.

36
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,190
(Trying to scare me?)

37
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:26,150
(I've been married three times.)

38
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,680
(I know all about)

39
00:02:27,910 --> 00:02:28,910
(these rich-family secrets.)

40
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,520
Ye Lang and I

41
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,710
grew up together.

42
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:35,080
Then he was brought back
as an illegitimate son

43
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:37,080
and forced to live under their roof

44
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,240
in this devouring mansion.

45
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,590
His health was never good after that,

46
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:44,960
and they suddenly announced
that he was brain-dead.

47
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,190
I didn't even get to see him one last time.

48
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,590
The Li family
has so many medical institutions,

49
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,240
couldn't they find even one doctor

50
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:53,150
who could cure him?

51
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,030
Well.

52
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,710
With so many

53
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,310
doctors and hospitals,

54
00:02:58,590 --> 00:03:00,030
it would be a pain to investigate.

55
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,470
Not really.

56
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,310
In Master Li's study,
there's a system

57
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:07,360
containing medical records
from every hospital in Manlong.

58
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,310
Forget finding just one doctor,

59
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:12,150
you could even track every visitor

60
00:03:13,470 --> 00:03:14,800
who has entered those hospitals.

61
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,280
(As long as I can hack the system,)

62
00:03:18,470 --> 00:03:20,030
(I can definitely find Xiaodi.)

63
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,120
Ms. Murong.

64
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:26,120
Do you know what Ye Lang likes to eat?

65
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,470
Well,

66
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:33,030
Lang loves snowflake crisps most.

67
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:36,310
When Auntie Ye Mei coaxed him
into taking his medicine...

68
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:38,190
Thanks for the coffee, Ms. Murong.

69
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:39,560
I'll be sure

70
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,630
to repay you another day.

71
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:46,240
(This maid outfit)

72
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,910
(does make it easier to slip in.)

73
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,230
How dare you!

74
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,600
Master's study

75
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,480
isn't a place you can just walk into.

76
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,750
You're

77
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,920
Ms. Jiang?

78
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:30,000
What did you do to the lock with your phone?

79
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:31,870
Trying to steal something?

80
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,510
Watch your words.

81
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,720
You can't just accuse me like that.

82
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,720
I just got lost.

83
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:44,390
You're quite the actress, aren't you?

84
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,600
First a witch,

85
00:04:51,270 --> 00:04:53,070
now a maid,

86
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:55,830
you've got plenty of tricks.

87
00:04:56,310 --> 00:04:57,150
Ms. Jiang,

88
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,750
this time,

89
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:00,240
who are you trying to seduce?

90
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:02,870
Ms. Murong Xue got me this outfit.

91
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:04,630
Is there a problem?

92
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,040
Search her.

93
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,390
This door lock

94
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,950
can only be opened

95
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:14,360
with the fingerprints of the master

96
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:16,040
or the two young masters.

97
00:05:16,870 --> 00:05:18,310
This shameless woman

98
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:20,310
must be trying to tamper with it!

99
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,560
Search her.

100
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,840
Stop!

101
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,000
What are you doing?

102
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,320
Oops!

103
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:39,190
It slipped.

104
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:42,710
This...

105
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,870
This is Young Master's medicine.

106
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,240
Never mind.

107
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,160
I'll make Ye Lang a new one.

108
00:05:48,650 --> 00:05:49,510
After all,

109
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:52,480
a wife should take care of her husband.

110
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:55,040
Butler Zhong,

111
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,920
please take good care of the madam.

112
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,600
(The Li family is such a mess.)

113
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:02,390
(Once I find which hospital Xiaodi is in,)

114
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:04,510
(I need to leave this awful place.)

115
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:11,750
Let's see how long you can keep this up.

116
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,680
You'll end up being fertilizer.

117
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,000
Young Master.

118
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:22,040
Time for your medicine.

119
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,070
Where did you go?

120
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:30,680
Why are you dressed like that?

121
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,040
I went to the kitchen

122
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,600
to prepare your medicine.

123
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,480
To nourish

124
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,430
your

125
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:38,270
body.

126
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,510
Coming in dressed like this,

127
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,520
what are you up to?

128
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:58,920
I heard the Li family has strict rules,

129
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,270
I just want you

130
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,040
to teach me a little more.

131
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:11,580
♪Bit by bit, marking you with kisses♪

132
00:07:12,130 --> 00:07:15,840
♪Like shadows entwined in the night♪

133
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,060
♪You are mine♪

134
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:21,860
♪Right now, I want you completely♪

135
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:28,610
♪Bit by bit, leaving traces behind♪

136
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:32,740
♪I love you, with no limits♪

137
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,840
♪Crimson bite marks♪

138
00:07:35,090 --> 00:07:38,240
♪Like I need you, and can't stop♪

139
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,310
Why did you make snowflake crisps?

140
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,600
You don't like it?

141
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,960
I like it.

142
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:47,480
I like

143
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:51,790
anything you make.

144
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,000
When I was little and had to take medicine,

145
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:57,240
my mom made snowflake crisps too.

146
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,160
So, is this snowflake crisp good?

147
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:02,720
If you like it,

148
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,680
I'll make it for you every day.

149
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:08,910
Young Master,

150
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,630
it's time for your medicine.

151
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,840
Niannian,

152
00:08:23,070 --> 00:08:23,910
for the rest of your life,

153
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:25,950
you can't leave me again.

154
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,750
Okay,

155
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,000
I won't leave you.

156
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:34,710
Young Master,

157
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:37,200
drink your medicine now.

158
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,230
Look, it's all your fault.

159
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,320
My clothes are wet,

160
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:44,790
yours too.

161
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,510
You'll catch a cold wearing this.

162
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:47,670
I'll help you take it off

163
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:50,200
and send it to the laundry.

164
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:51,750
Okay.

165
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:52,750
Get up.

166
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,000
What are you doing?

167
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,440
You scared me!

168
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:50,450
Get out.

169
00:09:50,470 --> 00:09:51,510
I need to change.

170
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:52,960
Need a hand?

171
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,480
Just go out.

172
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:57,000
That medicine made me all sticky.

173
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,080
I need to rinse off.

174
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:08,200
Come on, get out.

175
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,510
I need to wash up.

176
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,670
Hurry.

177
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,550
Jiang Niannian.

178
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,870
I won't repeat my previous life's mistake.

179
00:11:05,180 --> 00:11:41,540
(Previous Life)

180
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,870
The wedding's about to start.

181
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:43,960
Why're you here now?

182
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,750
I haven't seen you for 24 hours.

183
00:11:47,630 --> 00:11:48,670
If I didn't see you soon,

184
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,550
I felt like I'd die.

185
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,320
Niannian.

186
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:57,670
This feels like a dream.

187
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,480
From now on,

188
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:01,120
let's never be apart again.

189
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,680
Niannian.

190
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,080
It turns out

191
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,150
that when people are truly happy,

192
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,510
they can actually feel pain.

193
00:12:15,030 --> 00:12:16,150
Go to hell.

194
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:29,630
(In my previous life,
I loved you with all my heart.)

195
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:32,960
(Yet you killed me on our wedding day.)

196
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,960
(Jiang Niannian.)

197
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:37,960
(Why did you do that?)

198
00:12:39,620 --> 00:12:53,540
(This life The day Ye Lang Was Reborn)

199
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:54,600
(Could it be)

200
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,670
(I've been reborn?)

201
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,040
Ye Lang.

202
00:13:13,510 --> 00:13:14,360
Are you okay?

203
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:16,320
Do you feel unwell?

204
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,840
Where are we?

205
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,320
This is the funeral of Zhou Chen,
chairman of the Zhou Group.

206
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:24,150
He supplied
the Li family's medical equipment.

207
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:37,270
How could it be her?

208
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:40,110
You know her?

209
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,750
Zhou Chen was her third husband.

210
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,600
I heard the first two

211
00:13:45,270 --> 00:13:46,360
both died after marrying her.

212
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:48,360
(Jiang Niannian.)

213
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:51,030
(I never imagined)

214
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:52,790
(we'd already met before.)

215
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:56,990
Ye Lang.

216
00:13:57,150 --> 00:13:58,550
The ceremony isn't over,
where you going?

217
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,870
He has more inheritance than the last man.

218
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:03,150
The more Jiang Niannian marries,
the richer I get!

219
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:04,910
Don't gamble it all away.

220
00:14:04,910 --> 00:14:06,960
Qingqing needs money overseas too.

221
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:07,800
No worries.

222
00:14:31,980 --> 00:14:33,700
(Organ Donation Agreement)

223
00:14:33,700 --> 00:14:34,300
(Jiang Xiaodi)

224
00:14:37,380 --> 00:14:38,980
(Zheng Lu)

225
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,630
Once she enters the Li family,

226
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:44,960
she'll be mine.

227
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:46,750
As for her brother,

228
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,270
get the surgery done ASAP.

229
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:50,910
Don't forget what you promised me.

230
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,510
Jiang Niannian.

231
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,200
This life,

232
00:15:10,390 --> 00:15:13,080
I won't let the tragedy
of our past repeat itself.

233
00:15:32,130 --> 00:15:38,720
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

234
00:15:40,530 --> 00:15:46,740
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

235
00:15:47,290 --> 00:15:54,290
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

236
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:57,510
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

237
00:15:57,510 --> 00:16:02,510
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

238
00:16:02,510 --> 00:16:06,740
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

239
00:16:07,250 --> 00:16:11,180
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

240
00:16:11,230 --> 00:16:15,020
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

241
00:16:15,020 --> 00:16:20,770
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

242
00:16:20,770 --> 00:16:25,090
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

243
00:16:25,130 --> 00:16:28,950
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

244
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:33,450
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

245
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:38,310
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

246
00:16:38,710 --> 00:16:45,250
♪Life finds its way again♪

